These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, poker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, june
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski
1. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
3. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Game      | poker     | monopoly      |
| Birthday          | june | july    |
| Cigar         | aristoff   | dannemann |
| Transport   | boat  | jet-ski      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, cycling
There 2 different types of food: peach, lemon
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, soul
House: modern, palace
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
2. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
3. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
4. the modern house is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Sport    | skateboarding        | cycling    |
| Food       | peach         | lemon |
| Music-Genre         | soul | metal   |
| House   | modern               | palace  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, november
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, cooking
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, van
1. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Birthday   | march       | november |
| Hobby   | drawing       | cooking    |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Transport           | trike        | van   |

