.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, august
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, climbing
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
1. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Birthday         | august | october  |
| Color           | aquamarine  | lavender |
| Sport   | climbing | tennis   |
| Beverage     | tea   | coffee |

