.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: radish, grapefruit
2 different pets are kept: mouse, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the person eating radish is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | baking | collecting |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | mirinda     |
| Food         | radish  | grapefruit    |
| Pet     | fish     | mouse       |

