The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, adventure
1. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Hobby          | drawing         | puzzles    |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | sprite   |
| Game   | billiard   | mah-jongg    |
| Movie-Genre     | animation         | adventure |

 